"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641006437,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"ZqFk6pr-H5pMtoStdjpFpDOwUqKhF1BL-ybL9TyS01Y\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x191ABBF46417f32D0f4b7DC367E0565103c18525\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"jHEdNgWfpt5EpU_jUGGKvKdUeKTcW6UUrnFFT0OE0Wc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Ntxfw2Bchz20ESnyD445hggJw745y9XyQFCJwqiqm_w\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Y1Pe4_Zq5W7EptqZ9RByaFvFXLNafu7PPIh8UIthjGv0q3IvXq8xnFpt8weLxb3DySkOgVwMCoJY9j38IkrTOA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x680c3eb8acea772c5ca765f7c81b373982c179d5008dbe0369cc1a3dfa0a02ed0ec60e54b3641b27b5687136421ae17e6f45b2072934dfcf888cbc05b4f091a11b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"jHEdNgWfpt5EpU_jUGGKvKdUeKTcW6UUrnFFT0OE0Wc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Ntxfw2Bchz20ESnyD445hggJw745y9XyQFCJwqiqm_w\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi